{"tid":2100624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国下令：不得自創門派及自封大師","createTime":"2020-07-09T07:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T01:51:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":224,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"655d25abd97a62c1edcc1f52f10948b015783d6e","tid":2100624,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"中國武術協會發出《關於加強行業自律弘揚武術文化的倡議書》，要求習武之人「提升武德修養，遵守職業道德」，不得隨意自創拳種及門派，強調武術之人要根據《中國武術段位制》去評價武術水平，不得自封「大師」、「掌門」、「嫡傳」等稱號。《倡議書》提到，支持習武者參加武術競技比賽和交流，但不得參加「不分項目、性別、年齡、體重級別」等不規範賽事，並嚴禁習武者以「拜師收徒」、「賀壽慶典」等名義，炒作斂財。<br />\n<br />\n68歲自稱「混元形意太極掌門人」的馬保國，5月中曾經與業餘選手在擂台對賽，結果不足30秒就被對手3度擊倒，昏迷送院，引起討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346223/中國武術協會不得自創門派及自封大師\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2346223%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%A6%E8%A1%93%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E8%87%AA%E5%89%B5%E9%96%80%E6%B4%BE%E5%8F%8A%E8%87%AA%E5%B0%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%AB&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=8bc9371a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346223/中國武術協會不得自創門派及自封大師</a>"},{"pid":"78f77128650ff3f793560e8e8602356ab5991c2e","tid":2100624,"uid":31370,"like":154,"dislike":0,"score":154,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:38:05.000Z","msg":"國安師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfb08ad24bbf2c2f692a6bf32d8b31a06d688be","tid":2100624,"uid":37487,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:38:06.000Z","msg":"識自慰大師"},{"pid":"213ee7b883c97ad31df391fe14c9dd3e5634b772","tid":2100624,"uid":71237,"like":94,"dislike":1,"score":93,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:39:19.000Z","msg":"咁點解界定中國武術？<br />\n創立西洋武術門派得唔得？"},{"pid":"068df6d58f5dadb52263f8cd115580716fb1b0db","tid":2100624,"uid":24036,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:40:12.000Z","msg":"自封死屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/do